[5] Indonesia (South Sulaweisi)
Date: Wed 5 Dec 2007
Source: Fajar [in Indonesian, trans. & summ., edited]
<http://www.fajar.co.id/news.php?newsid=48002>


The number of dengue patients in RSU Wahidin Sudirohusodo continued
to increase, on the basis of review of the number of patients from
October to the end of November [2007]. The number of dengue patients
in October totalled 54, in November was 100 and in December to date
(5 Dec 2007) there have been 5 cases.

